// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1007 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: a40ebe70-67d8-5ad8-94d2-7958ce4c93bc

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:13.10*")
